{
  "book": "1nephi",
  "bookName": "1 Nephi",
  "chapter": 11,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "Samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 448.674,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 2.276,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For then after I had desired to know",
      "verse": "11:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 2.456,
      "end": 4.639,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the things that my father had seen,",
      "verse": "11:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 4.819,
      "end": 8.209,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and believing that the Lord was able to make them known to me,",
      "verse": "11:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 8.389,
      "end": 10.897,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "as I sat pondering in my heart",
      "verse": "11:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 11.077,
      "end": 13.724,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I was caught away in the Spirit of the Lord,",
      "verse": "11:1",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 13.904,
      "end": 16.272,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yes, into a very high mountain,",
      "verse": "11:1",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 16.452,
      "end": 18.402,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which I never had before seen,",
      "verse": "11:1",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 18.582,
      "end": 21.276,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and upon which I never had before set my foot.",
      "verse": "11:1",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 21.956,
      "end": 23.581,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the Spirit said to me:",
      "verse": "11:2",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 23.761,
      "end": 25.433,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, what do you desire?",
      "verse": "11:2",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 26.113,
      "end": 27.32,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I said:",
      "verse": "11:3",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 27.5,
      "end": 30.565,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I desire to behold the things which my father saw.",
      "verse": "11:3",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 31.245,
      "end": 32.87,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the Spirit said to me:",
      "verse": "11:4",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 33.05,
      "end": 37.276,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Do you believe that your father saw the tree of which he has spoken?",
      "verse": "11:4",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 37.956,
      "end": 39.163,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I said:",
      "verse": "11:5",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 39.343,
      "end": 42.872,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Indeed, you know that I believe all the words of my father.",
      "verse": "11:5",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 43.552,
      "end": 46.06,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And when I had spoken these words,",
      "verse": "11:6",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 46.24,
      "end": 48.608,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the Spirit cried with a loud voice, saying:",
      "verse": "11:6",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 48.788,
      "end": 51.249,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Hosanna to the Lord, the most high God;",
      "verse": "11:6",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 51.429,
      "end": 53.797,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for he is God over all the earth,",
      "verse": "11:6",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 53.977,
      "end": 55.742,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "indeed, even above all.",
      "verse": "11:6",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 55.922,
      "end": 57.78,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And blessed are you, Nephi,",
      "verse": "11:6",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 57.96,
      "end": 61.025,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because you believe in the Son of the most high God;",
      "verse": "11:6",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 61.205,
      "end": 64.642,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so, you shall behold the things which you have desired.",
      "verse": "11:6",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 65.322,
      "end": 68.898,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And behold this thing shall be given to you for a sign,",
      "verse": "11:7",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 69.078,
      "end": 71.4,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that after you have seen the tree",
      "verse": "11:7",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 71.58,
      "end": 74.691,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which bore the fruit which your father tasted,",
      "verse": "11:7",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 74.871,
      "end": 78.354,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "you shall also behold a man descending out of heaven",
      "verse": "11:7",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 78.534,
      "end": 80.252,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and him shall you witness;",
      "verse": "11:7",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 80.432,
      "end": 82.522,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and after you have witnessed him",
      "verse": "11:7",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 82.702,
      "end": 86.092,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "you shall bear record that it is the Son of God.",
      "verse": "11:7",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 86.772,
      "end": 88.583,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then the Spirit said to me:",
      "verse": "11:8",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 88.763,
      "end": 89.599,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Look!",
      "verse": "11:8",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 89.779,
      "end": 91.869,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I looked and saw a tree;",
      "verse": "11:8",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 92.049,
      "end": 95.114,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it was like to the tree which my father had seen;",
      "verse": "11:8",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 95.294,
      "end": 97.662,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the beauty of it was far beyond,",
      "verse": "11:8",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 97.842,
      "end": 99.56,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yes, great of all beauty;",
      "verse": "11:8",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 99.74,
      "end": 105.034,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the whiteness of it exceeded the whiteness of the driven snow.",
      "verse": "11:8",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 105.714,
      "end": 107.711,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then after I had seen the tree,",
      "verse": "11:9",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 107.891,
      "end": 109.424,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I said to the Spirit:",
      "verse": "11:9",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 109.604,
      "end": 112.112,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I behold you have shown to me the tree",
      "verse": "11:9",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 112.292,
      "end": 114.15,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which is precious above all.",
      "verse": "11:9",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 114.83,
      "end": 116.223,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he said to me:",
      "verse": "11:10",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 116.403,
      "end": 117.657,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "What do you desire?",
      "verse": "11:10",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 118.337,
      "end": 119.916,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I said to him:",
      "verse": "11:11",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 120.096,
      "end": 122.511,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "To know the interpretation of it\u2014",
      "verse": "11:11",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 122.691,
      "end": 125.292,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I spoke to him as a man speaks;",
      "verse": "11:11",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 125.472,
      "end": 128.63,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I saw that he was in the form of a man;",
      "verse": "11:11",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 128.81,
      "end": 132.061,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yet but, I knew that it was the Spirit of the Lord;",
      "verse": "11:11",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 132.241,
      "end": 135.213,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he spoke to me as a man speaks with another.",
      "verse": "11:11",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 135.893,
      "end": 137.518,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then he said to me:",
      "verse": "11:12",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 137.698,
      "end": 138.534,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Look!",
      "verse": "11:12",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 138.714,
      "end": 141.965,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I looked as if to look upon him, and I saw him not;",
      "verse": "11:12",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 142.145,
      "end": 144.513,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for he had gone from before my presence.",
      "verse": "11:12",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 145.193,
      "end": 147.283,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I looked",
      "verse": "11:13",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 147.463,
      "end": 150.017,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and saw the great city of Jerusalem,",
      "verse": "11:13",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 150.197,
      "end": 151.776,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also other cities.",
      "verse": "11:13",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 151.956,
      "end": 154.278,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I saw the city of Nazareth;",
      "verse": "11:13",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 154.458,
      "end": 157.384,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and in the city of Nazareth I saw a virgin,",
      "verse": "11:13",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 157.564,
      "end": 159.561,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and she was very fair and white.",
      "verse": "11:13",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 160.241,
      "end": 162.377,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I saw the heavens open;",
      "verse": "11:14",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 162.557,
      "end": 165.111,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and an angel came down and stood before me;",
      "verse": "11:14",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 165.291,
      "end": 166.684,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he said to me:",
      "verse": "11:14",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 166.864,
      "end": 168.489,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Nephi, what do you behold?",
      "verse": "11:14",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 169.169,
      "end": 170.748,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I said to him:",
      "verse": "11:15",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 170.928,
      "end": 172.089,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "A virgin,",
      "verse": "11:15",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 172.269,
      "end": 175.427,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "most beautiful and fair above all other virgins.",
      "verse": "11:15",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 176.107,
      "end": 177.5,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he said to me:",
      "verse": "11:16",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 177.68,
      "end": 179.956,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Do you know the condescension of God?",
      "verse": "11:16",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 180.636,
      "end": 182.215,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I said to him:",
      "verse": "11:17",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 182.395,
      "end": 184.485,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I know that he loves his children;",
      "verse": "11:17",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 184.665,
      "end": 187.544,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but, I do not know the meaning of all things.",
      "verse": "11:17",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 188.224,
      "end": 189.617,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he said to me:",
      "verse": "11:18",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 189.797,
      "end": 191.701,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, the virgin whom you see",
      "verse": "11:18",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 191.881,
      "end": 194.11,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "is the mother of the Son of God,",
      "verse": "11:18",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 194.29,
      "end": 196.194,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "after the manner of the flesh.",
      "verse": "11:18",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 196.874,
      "end": 199.985,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I saw that she was carried away in the Spirit;",
      "verse": "11:19",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 200.165,
      "end": 204.298,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and after she had been carried away in the Spirit for the space of a time",
      "verse": "11:19",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 204.478,
      "end": 206.196,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the angel spoke to me, saying:",
      "verse": "11:19",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 206.376,
      "end": 207.212,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Look!",
      "verse": "11:19",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 207.892,
      "end": 212.443,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I looked and saw the virgin again, bearing a child in her arms.",
      "verse": "11:20",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 213.123,
      "end": 214.748,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the angel said to me:",
      "verse": "11:21",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 214.928,
      "end": 216.693,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold the Lamb of God,",
      "verse": "11:21",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 216.873,
      "end": 219.892,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "indeed, even the Son of the Eternal Father!",
      "verse": "11:21",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 220.072,
      "end": 223.23,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Do you know the meaning of the tree which your father saw?",
      "verse": "11:21",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 223.91,
      "end": 225.86,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I answered him, saying:",
      "verse": "11:22",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 226.04,
      "end": 228.037,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Indeed, it is the love of God,",
      "verse": "11:22",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 228.217,
      "end": 230.167,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which sheds itself abroad",
      "verse": "11:22",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 230.347,
      "end": 232.808,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in the hearts of the children of men;",
      "verse": "11:22",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 232.988,
      "end": 236.239,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so, it is the most desirable above all things.",
      "verse": "11:22",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 236.919,
      "end": 238.916,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he spoke to me, saying:",
      "verse": "11:23",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 239.096,
      "end": 241.882,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Indeed, and the most joyous to the soul.",
      "verse": "11:23",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 242.562,
      "end": 245.441,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after he had said these words, he said to me:",
      "verse": "11:24",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 245.621,
      "end": 246.457,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Look!",
      "verse": "11:24",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 246.637,
      "end": 251.42,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I looked, and I saw the Son of God going forth among the children of men;",
      "verse": "11:24",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 251.6,
      "end": 255.083,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw many fall down at his feet and worship him.",
      "verse": "11:24",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 255.763,
      "end": 258.085,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I saw that the rod of iron,",
      "verse": "11:25",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 258.265,
      "end": 260.076,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which my father had seen,",
      "verse": "11:25",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 260.256,
      "end": 261.835,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "was the word of God,",
      "verse": "11:25",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 262.015,
      "end": 264.894,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which led to the fountain of living waters,",
      "verse": "11:25",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 265.074,
      "end": 267.489,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or to the tree of life; which waters",
      "verse": "11:25",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 267.669,
      "end": 270.363,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "are a representation of the love of God;",
      "verse": "11:25",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 270.543,
      "end": 272.865,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I also saw that the tree of life",
      "verse": "11:25",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 273.045,
      "end": 275.646,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "was a representation of the love of God.",
      "verse": "11:25",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 276.326,
      "end": 278.184,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the angel said to me again:",
      "verse": "11:26",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 278.364,
      "end": 280.732,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Look and behold the condescension of God!",
      "verse": "11:26",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 281.412,
      "end": 284.245,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I looked and saw the Redeemer of the world,",
      "verse": "11:27",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 284.425,
      "end": 286.422,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "of whom my father had spoken;",
      "verse": "11:27",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
      "start": 286.602,
      "end": 288.413,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I also saw the prophet",
      "verse": "11:27",
      "lineIndex": 112
    },
    {
      "start": 288.593,
      "end": 290.822,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who should prepare the way before him.",
      "verse": "11:27",
      "lineIndex": 113
    },
    {
      "start": 291.002,
      "end": 292.999,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the Lamb of God went forth",
      "verse": "11:27",
      "lineIndex": 114
    },
    {
      "start": 293.179,
      "end": 294.851,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and was baptized of him;",
      "verse": "11:27",
      "lineIndex": 115
    },
    {
      "start": 295.031,
      "end": 296.703,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and after he was baptized,",
      "verse": "11:27",
      "lineIndex": 116
    },
    {
      "start": 296.883,
      "end": 298.508,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I saw the heavens open,",
      "verse": "11:27",
      "lineIndex": 117
    },
    {
      "start": 298.688,
      "end": 301.196,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the Holy Ghost come down out of heaven",
      "verse": "11:27",
      "lineIndex": 118
    },
    {
      "start": 301.376,
      "end": 303.93,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and abide upon him in the form of a dove.",
      "verse": "11:27",
      "lineIndex": 119
    },
    {
      "start": 304.61,
      "end": 306.421,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I saw that he went forth",
      "verse": "11:28",
      "lineIndex": 120
    },
    {
      "start": 306.601,
      "end": 309.573,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "ministering to the people, in power and great glory;",
      "verse": "11:28",
      "lineIndex": 121
    },
    {
      "start": 309.753,
      "end": 313.05,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the multitudes were gathered together to hear him;",
      "verse": "11:28",
      "lineIndex": 122
    },
    {
      "start": 313.23,
      "end": 316.249,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw that they cast him out from among them.",
      "verse": "11:28",
      "lineIndex": 123
    },
    {
      "start": 316.929,
      "end": 319.53,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I also saw twelve others following him.",
      "verse": "11:29",
      "lineIndex": 124
    },
    {
      "start": 319.71,
      "end": 322.496,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then they were carried away in the Spirit",
      "verse": "11:29",
      "lineIndex": 125
    },
    {
      "start": 322.676,
      "end": 324.209,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from before my face,",
      "verse": "11:29",
      "lineIndex": 126
    },
    {
      "start": 324.389,
      "end": 325.922,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw them not.",
      "verse": "11:29",
      "lineIndex": 127
    },
    {
      "start": 326.602,
      "end": 329.017,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then the angel spoke to me again, saying:",
      "verse": "11:30",
      "lineIndex": 128
    },
    {
      "start": 329.197,
      "end": 330.033,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Look!",
      "verse": "11:30",
      "lineIndex": 129
    },
    {
      "start": 330.213,
      "end": 333.232,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I looked, and I saw the heavens open again,",
      "verse": "11:30",
      "lineIndex": 130
    },
    {
      "start": 333.412,
      "end": 336.756,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw angels descending upon the children of men;",
      "verse": "11:30",
      "lineIndex": 131
    },
    {
      "start": 336.936,
      "end": 338.701,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they ministered to them.",
      "verse": "11:30",
      "lineIndex": 132
    },
    {
      "start": 339.381,
      "end": 341.564,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he spoke to me again, saying:",
      "verse": "11:31",
      "lineIndex": 133
    },
    {
      "start": 341.744,
      "end": 342.58,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Look!",
      "verse": "11:31",
      "lineIndex": 134
    },
    {
      "start": 342.76,
      "end": 345.5,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I looked, and I saw the Lamb of God",
      "verse": "11:31",
      "lineIndex": 135
    },
    {
      "start": 345.68,
      "end": 348.002,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "going forth among the children of men.",
      "verse": "11:31",
      "lineIndex": 136
    },
    {
      "start": 348.182,
      "end": 350.829,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I saw multitudes of people who were sick,",
      "verse": "11:31",
      "lineIndex": 137
    },
    {
      "start": 351.009,
      "end": 353.935,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and who were afflicted with all manner of diseases,",
      "verse": "11:31",
      "lineIndex": 138
    },
    {
      "start": 354.115,
      "end": 356.53,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and with devils and unclean spirits;",
      "verse": "11:31",
      "lineIndex": 139
    },
    {
      "start": 356.71,
      "end": 359.589,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the angel spoke and showed all these things to me.",
      "verse": "11:31",
      "lineIndex": 140
    },
    {
      "start": 359.769,
      "end": 363.298,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And they were healed by the power of the Lamb of God;",
      "verse": "11:31",
      "lineIndex": 141
    },
    {
      "start": 363.478,
      "end": 366.729,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the devils and the unclean spirits were cast out.",
      "verse": "11:31",
      "lineIndex": 142
    },
    {
      "start": 367.409,
      "end": 369.824,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then the angel spoke to me again, saying:",
      "verse": "11:32",
      "lineIndex": 144
    },
    {
      "start": 370.004,
      "end": 370.84,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Look!",
      "verse": "11:32",
      "lineIndex": 145
    },
    {
      "start": 371.02,
      "end": 373.528,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I looked and saw the Lamb of God,",
      "verse": "11:32",
      "lineIndex": 146
    },
    {
      "start": 373.708,
      "end": 375.658,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he was taken by the people;",
      "verse": "11:32",
      "lineIndex": 147
    },
    {
      "start": 375.838,
      "end": 379.321,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yes, the Son of the everlasting God was judged of the world;",
      "verse": "11:32",
      "lineIndex": 148
    },
    {
      "start": 379.501,
      "end": 381.219,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw and bear record.",
      "verse": "11:32",
      "lineIndex": 149
    },
    {
      "start": 381.899,
      "end": 385.754,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I, Nephi, saw that he was lifted up upon the cross",
      "verse": "11:33",
      "lineIndex": 150
    },
    {
      "start": 385.934,
      "end": 388.256,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and killed for the sins of the world.",
      "verse": "11:33",
      "lineIndex": 151
    },
    {
      "start": 388.936,
      "end": 390.654,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after he was killed",
      "verse": "11:34",
      "lineIndex": 152
    },
    {
      "start": 390.834,
      "end": 393.156,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I saw the multitudes of the earth,",
      "verse": "11:34",
      "lineIndex": 153
    },
    {
      "start": 393.336,
      "end": 396.215,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they were gathered together",
      "verse": "11:34",
      "lineIndex": 154
    },
    {
      "start": 396.395,
      "end": 399.321,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to fight against the apostles of the Lamb;",
      "verse": "11:34",
      "lineIndex": 155
    },
    {
      "start": 399.501,
      "end": 402.566,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for thus were the twelve called by the angel of the Lord.",
      "verse": "11:34",
      "lineIndex": 156
    },
    {
      "start": 403.246,
      "end": 406.636,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the multitude of the earth was gathered together;",
      "verse": "11:35",
      "lineIndex": 157
    },
    {
      "start": 406.816,
      "end": 410.485,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw that they were in a large and spacious building,",
      "verse": "11:35",
      "lineIndex": 158
    },
    {
      "start": 410.665,
      "end": 412.755,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "like to the building which my father saw.",
      "verse": "11:35",
      "lineIndex": 159
    },
    {
      "start": 412.935,
      "end": 416.0,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the angel of the Lord spoke to me again, saying:",
      "verse": "11:35",
      "lineIndex": 160
    },
    {
      "start": 416.18,
      "end": 418.781,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold the world and the wisdom of it;",
      "verse": "11:35",
      "lineIndex": 161
    },
    {
      "start": 418.961,
      "end": 422.165,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yes, behold the house of Israel has gathered together",
      "verse": "11:35",
      "lineIndex": 162
    },
    {
      "start": 422.345,
      "end": 425.503,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to fight against the twelve apostles of the Lamb.",
      "verse": "11:35",
      "lineIndex": 163
    },
    {
      "start": 426.183,
      "end": 428.18,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I saw and bear record,",
      "verse": "11:36",
      "lineIndex": 164
    },
    {
      "start": 428.36,
      "end": 431.75,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the great and spacious building was the pride of the world;",
      "verse": "11:36",
      "lineIndex": 165
    },
    {
      "start": 431.93,
      "end": 433.091,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it fell,",
      "verse": "11:36",
      "lineIndex": 166
    },
    {
      "start": 433.271,
      "end": 435.732,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the fall of it was very great.",
      "verse": "11:36",
      "lineIndex": 167
    },
    {
      "start": 435.912,
      "end": 438.977,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the angel of the Lord spoke to me again, saying:",
      "verse": "11:36",
      "lineIndex": 168
    },
    {
      "start": 439.157,
      "end": 441.479,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Thus shall be the destruction",
      "verse": "11:36",
      "lineIndex": 169
    },
    {
      "start": 441.659,
      "end": 444.353,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "of all nations, kindreds, tongues, and people,",
      "verse": "11:36",
      "lineIndex": 170
    },
    {
      "start": 444.533,
      "end": 448.016,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that shall fight against the twelve apostles of the Lamb.",
      "verse": "11:36",
      "lineIndex": 171
    }
  ]
}